# Result visibility rule

**The result is only ever known to the player AFTER the ball lands in the final slot.**

- Do not highlight the result slot until the ball has landed (e.g. `onLand` has fired / `landed` state is true).
- Do not update the displayed balance until the ball has landed (delay balance update to match animation landing time).
- Do not add the outcome to the Results list until the ball has landed.
- Any other UI that reveals the outcome (win amount, slot, etc.) must wait until the ball has landed.

The server outcome is available when the bet API returns, but the client must not reveal it to the player until the ball animation has reached the slot.
